'''Polyhaline''' is a salinity category term applied to [[brackish]] [[estuaries]] and other water bodies with a [[salinity]] of between 18 and 30 [[parts per thousand]]. It is the most dense saltwater type that is classified{{by whom?|date=April 2015}} as &#8220;brackish.&#8221;

